snippet.title: Empire of the Ants – Retail Editions Trailer
snippet.description:
Empire of the Ants arrives, November 7th, 2024, as an epic 3D Real-Time Strategy game for PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S.

🐜 Add the game to your Wishlist:
🐜 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2287330/Empire_of_the_Ants/ 
🐜 PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10007652 
🐜 Xbox : https://www.xbox.com/en-GB/games/store/empire-of-the-ants/9P82CBM74SRG/0010
🐜 Epic Games Store : https://store.epicgames.com/p/empire-of-the-ants-ffcba5
🐜 GOG : https://www.gog.com/en/game/empire_of_the_ants

Dive into the fascinating world of Empire of the Ants and lead your colony to glory! 🌿🐜

#bernardwerber #aventure #rts #ant #ants #gamers #trailer #physicaledition #steelbook

Follow Empire of the Ants on X (Twitter) to learn more: https://twitter.com/EmpireAntsGame 
Join the colony – we recently opened our subreddit! https://www.reddit.com/r/EmpireAntsGame/
